WEBVTT

00:03:59.640 --> 00:04:03.150
the signals from both 
the eyes will overlap,

00:04:03.150 --> 00:04:05.200
and we don’t have a choice over it.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:07.200
This is the sensation everybody will get.

00:04:08.240 --> 00:04:11.136
So this is the basic circuit everyone has.

00:04:11.160 --> 00:04:15.256
But every circuit is fine-tuned
differently for different people.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:19.136
Every skill is nurtured in the womb itself,

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:22.696
and it continues to progress
much after birth.

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:25.176
Every skill has its own timing.

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:30.856
Some of their circuits
are flexible, a little adjustable